This isolates your infrastructure.

ğŸ”§ Actions:
Go to VPC Dashboard â†’ Create VPC

Name: LovelySkins-VPC

IPv4 CIDR block: 10.0.0.0/16

Create Subnets:

2 Public subnets: 10.0.1.0/24, 10.0.2.0/24

2 Private subnets: 10.0.3.0/24, 10.0.4.0/24

